      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "## I'm a Node!\n\nI have:\n- A unique ID\n- A type (markdown)\n- Some data (this text)\n- Ports for connections\n\nNodes can be:\n- Markdown documents\n- Code snippets\n- Data structures\n- Custom types you define",
        "memo": "",
        "link": "",
        "html": "",
        "svg": ""
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "principles",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "Design Principles",
      "position": {
        "x": -200,
        "y": 600
      },
      "width": 360,
      "height": 320,
      "color": "#1976d2",
      "ports": [
        {
          "id": "in",
          "label": "In",
          "direction": "input",
          "dataType": "flow",
          "position": {
            "side": "top",
            "offset": 0.5
          }
        }
      ],
      "inputs": [
        {
          "key": "in",
          "label": "In",
          "type": "flow"
        }
      ],
      "outputs": [],
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "## Design Principles\n\n### Continuity over Convenience\nPreserve graph history and identity. Small diffs build trust.\n\n### Intent before Action\nUnderstand purpose through the Manifest before mutating.\n\n### Semantics over Presentation\nValidate meaning, not styling. Missing positions are warnings, not errors.\n\n### Explicit over Implicit\nDeclare ports, types, and IDs. Don't guess.\n\n### Contract-First\nRespect declared constraints and authority boundaries.",
        "memo": "",
        "link": "",
        "html": "",
        "svg": ""
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "try-it",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "Try It Yourself",
      "position": {
        "x": 250,
        "y": 600
      },
      "width": 360,
      "height": 280,
      "color": "#1976d2",
      "ports": [
        {
          "id": "in",
          "label": "In",
          "direction": "input",
          "dataType": "flow",
          "position": {
            "side": "top",
            "offset": 0.5
          }
        }
      ],
      "inputs": [
        {
          "key": "in",
          "label": "In",
          "type": "flow"
        }
      ],
      "outputs": [],
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "## Ready to Build?\n\nTry creating your first node:\n\n```json\n{\n  \"action\": \"createNodes\",\n  \"nodes\": [{\n    \"id\": \"my-first-node\",\n    \"type\": \"markdown\",\n    \"label\": \"My First Node\",\n    \"data\": {\n      \"markdown\": \"Hello Twilite!\"\n    },\n    \"ports\": [\n      { \"id\": \"in\", \"direction\": \"input\" },\n      { \"id\": \"out\", \"direction\": \"output\" }\n    ]\n  }]\n}\n```\n\nRemember: nodes first, edges second!",
        "memo": "",
        "link": "",
        "html": "",
        "svg": ""
      }
    },
