      "data": {
        "markdown": "## Learn More\n\n### Documentation\n- Core principles\n- Node type reference\n- Edge type catalog\n- Manifest specification\n- Command reference\n\n### Examples\n- Simple workflows\n- Knowledge graphs\n- Project planning\n- Documentation sites\n\n**Questions?** Just ask!",
        "memo": "",
